# pip-audit ignore list for the CI security job (.github/workflows/ci.yml).
#
# Format: one CVE/GHSA ID per line, with an optional rationale comment after
# the ID. Blank lines and lines starting with `#` are ignored.
#
# Example:
# GHSA-1234-abcd-5678  # vendored fix landed in our pinned commit; safe to ignore
#
# Prefer fixing the underlying CVE by bumping the dep. Use this file only for
# accepted-risk items or for false positives where you're waiting on an
# upstream fix.
